rows.label: tlk70000057_02_msg0001
rows.name:
There's lotsa people here. Some of
them are from faraway places, too!

rows.label: tlk70000057_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Did you come here to get
away from scary people like
me 'n my brother did?

rows.label: tlk70000057_02_msg0003
rows.name:
I hope you get to go back
to your families soon.

rows.label: tlk70000057_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Everyone's got people they miss. I
hope you get to see yours soon.
